    "patch_code": "if (!callNode.isNoSideEffectsCall() && callNode.getNumChildren() > 0\n   && compiler != null && !compiler.hasRegExpGlobalReferences()) {\n   if (compiler.canSkipBuiltInFunctionWithoutSideEffects(callNode)) {\n     return false;\n   }\n \n  Node nameNode = callNode.getFirstChild();\n  if (nameNode.getType() == Token.DYNAMIC || nameNode.getType() == Token.GETPROP ) {\n    // Built-in getter or setter methods.\n    String methodName = nameNode.getLastChild().getString();\n    if ((compiler instanceof JSC).compiler instanceof JSC && ((JSC)compiler).isAllowedGetterSetterOrMethod(methodName)) {\n       return false;\n    }\n  }\n}\nreturn true;",
